WEBVTT

00:22.500 --> 00:23.960
准备好了吗？
You ready?

00:26.270 --> 00:28.500
没想到我会这么紧张
Didn't think l'd be this nervous.

00:33.970 --> 00:35.870
现在不做就永远不用做了
Now or never.

00:41.680 --> 00:44.170
好了，老大，走吧
All right, papi, let's do this.

00:45.090 --> 00:46.810
他在那里
He's over there.

00:57.400 --> 00:59.160
你一定就是麦可
You must be Michael.

00:59.330 --> 01:02.500
你的朋友费南多告诉我  你今天用得上我
Your friend Fernando tells me  you could use my services today.

01:02.670 --> 01:04.140
没错
very much so.

01:04.300 --> 01:07.640
我想那位就是你的另一半吧？
And l assume that's the other half  of your team?

01:16.720 --> 01:18.480
你看起来好美
You look beautiful.

01:19.920 --> 01:21.510
谢谢
Thank you.

01:26.190 --> 01:28.790
我想你想要简单一点
lt's my understanding you'd like  to keep this simple.

01:30.500 --> 01:33.520
我们总是把事情搞得很复杂
We've never actually managed  to keep anything simple.

01:33.700 --> 01:34.790
可以试看看
You can try.

01:35.300 --> 01:38.240
那我们开始好吗？
Well, let's begin then, shall we?

01:38.840 --> 01:39.970
各位亲朋好友
Family and friends...

01:40.140 --> 01:43.080
今天我们聚在这里一起祝贺
...we gather here  to celebrate the union...

01:43.240 --> 01:47.510
麦可史柯菲和莎拉丹奎迪永结同心
...between Michael Scofield  and Sara Tancredi.

02:19.050 --> 02:20.070
没错，老大
Oh, yeah, papi.

02:20.250 --> 02:23.510
她有波多黎各血统，你看看她
This one has Puerto Rican blood  in her, l think. Look at her.

02:42.870 --> 02:44.460
抱歉打扰你们的宴会
Sorry to break up the party.

02:44.640 --> 02:47.070
- 怎么回事？  - 我们有逮捕令
-What is going on?  -We have an arrest warrant.

02:47.240 --> 02:50.470
- 什么？  - 去问华府的保罗凯勒曼探员
-What?  -Talk to Agent Paul Kellerman in D.C.

02:50.640 --> 02:53.770
我们几个礼拜前就已经  跟联邦调查局解决好了这件事
We settled this with the Feds.  We settled this weeks ago.

02:53.950 --> 02:56.280
- 退后  - 我们已经被开释了
-Sir, back up.  -We were exonerated.

02:56.450 --> 02:58.150
- 退后  - 我们已经被开释了
-Sir, back up.  -We were exonerated!

02:58.520 --> 03:01.010
我们不是来找你，而是找她
We're not here for you.  We're here for her.

03:02.390 --> 03:04.910
她什么也没做，她毫无关系
She didn't do anything.  She wasn't involved.

03:05.090 --> 03:06.320
别闹事
Don't make this escalate.

03:06.630 --> 03:10.060
莎拉丹奎迪，你因谋杀  克利丝汀娜汉普顿被捕
Sara Tancredi, you're under arrest  for the murder of Christina Hampton.

03:10.630 --> 03:12.620
什么？她没有杀人
What? She didn't kill anyone.

03:12.800 --> 03:15.670
真有趣，监视录影划面  可不是这么说
Funny. Surveillance-camera footage  says different.

03:17.940 --> 03:19.530
麦可
Michael.

03:20.340 --> 03:21.570
- 这边走  - 麦可
-Right this way.  -Michael.

03:21.740 --> 03:23.330
- 请上第二台车  - 麦可
-Second car, please.  -Michael.

03:23.540 --> 03:25.240
- 发生什么事？  - 别靠过来
-What's going on?  -Back up, please.

03:31.590 --> 03:33.820
片名：越狱风云

03:37.790 --> 03:39.520
他们不许我见她
They're not gonna let me see her.

03:39.690 --> 03:42.920
如果你什么也不能做  凯勒曼为什么要你来？
Why did Kellerman send you  if you can't do anything?

03:43.860 --> 03:45.920
他们想拆散你们两个
They're trying to break both of you.

03:46.100 --> 03:48.660
她有被探访的权利
Look, she has a constitutional right  to visitation.

03:48.840 --> 03:51.360
我会拟订裁定送给法官签署
l'll draw up an order  and get it before a judge.

03:51.570 --> 03:53.440
你可以说是自卫吗？
Can you argue self-defense?

03:53.610 --> 03:54.870
怎么说？
How?

03:56.110 --> 03:58.630
现在没办法帮她
Anything that might help her  is out of frame.

03:58.810 --> 04:02.370
监视划面显示莎拉走上前  朝受害者开枪
Security camera only shows Sara  stepping up and firing at the victim.

04:03.150 --> 04:05.620
- 开枪啊，麦可  - 把枪放下
-Pull the trigger, Michael.  -Drop the gun.

04:06.390 --> 04:08.180
开不了枪
Misfire.

04:11.660 --> 04:13.630
- 她为公司工作  - 那是对你来说
-She worked for the Company.  -To you.

04:13.790 --> 04:16.460
对陪审团来说她是技术顾问  克利丝汀娜汉普顿
To a jury,  she's Christina Hampton, consultant.

04:16.630 --> 04:20.500
因为她太会隐藏真实身份  我们没办法证实
Because she was so good at hiding her  true identity, we can't prove otherwise.

04:21.540 --> 04:25.160
你们全都无罪开释  让执法单位面子挂不住
Look, you were all exonerated.  lt did not sit well with law enforcement.

04:25.340 --> 04:27.140
如果能让莎拉代罪  他们就会这么做
lf they can make Sara pay, they will.

04:27.540 --> 04:29.600
她会被判几年？
How much time is she looking at?

04:31.380 --> 04:33.240
二十五年或无期徒刑
Twenty-five to life.

04:37.480 --> 04:39.380
（迈阿密戴德监狱，女子监狱）

04:42.860 --> 04:45.260
（女舍，第三级）
Ladies, Level 3.

04:50.200 --> 04:53.260
你睡这
You, over here.

04:55.070 --> 04:57.000
你睡这
You, here.

04:59.840 --> 05:03.170
- 你睡这  - 没错
-You, here.  -That's right.

05:06.180 --> 05:07.200
这张是你的
This one's yours.

05:08.520 --> 05:10.780
我不应该被送到这里吧？
Aren't l supposed to be  in a different facility?

05:10.950 --> 05:12.010
就是这里
l don't think so.

05:12.190 --> 05:15.780
我还没被定罪，应该去看守所  这里是监狱
l haven't been convicted. l'm supposed  to be in a jail. This is prison.

05:15.960 --> 05:18.250
那里太挤了，预算又被砍
Overcrowding and budget cuts, fish.

05:18.430 --> 05:20.020
这边就是看守所
This is the jail.

05:20.190 --> 05:21.560
那边是监狱
That's the prison.

05:21.730 --> 05:24.160
放下就好
Just leave it there.

05:24.400 --> 05:26.660
代码九十九号
Code 99.

05:31.200 --> 05:32.730
怎么啦？
What's up, homey?

05:32.910 --> 05:34.370
要帮忙吗？
You need some help?

05:38.080 --> 05:41.780
需要的东西都有了吗？  你何不去帮她铺床
You got everything you need over there?  Why don't you go help make her bed.

05:43.120 --> 05:48.050
茉莉警官请到康乐室
Sergeant Malloy to rec room.  Sergeant Malloy to rec room.

05:49.890 --> 05:51.260
别让她们吓你
Don't let them spook you.

05:51.930 --> 05:54.620
- 她们就喜欢威吓人  - 她们很有一手
-They just like to intimidate.  -They're good at it.

05:55.430 --> 05:59.760
听着，监狱和看守所  混在一起真的很烂
Look, this jail-prison hybrid thing  is B.S.

06:01.330 --> 06:02.390
来吧
Come on.

06:02.570 --> 06:04.230
另一间几乎是空的
The other one's practically empty.

06:04.400 --> 06:06.900
你就安心的在那等开庭吧
You can ride it out  till your court date there.

06:07.240 --> 06:08.260
哪一间？
Which one?

06:08.440 --> 06:09.470
谢谢
Thank you.

06:27.990 --> 06:30.930
这里，这应该比较舒适
Here. This should be  a little bit more comfortable for you.

06:31.100 --> 06:32.720
好
Okay.

06:39.310 --> 06:40.430
怎么了？
What's going on?

06:42.040 --> 06:45.030
刚开始
You know, at first...

06:45.250 --> 06:46.770
我认不出你的名字
...l couldn't place your name.

06:46.950 --> 06:48.610
丹奎迪
Tancredi.

06:48.780 --> 06:50.270
听起来好耳熟
lt sounded so familiar.

06:50.980 --> 06:52.780
赫克来了认出你是谁
Then Hucks here, figured it out.

06:53.520 --> 06:56.790
我从报上记起你
l remembered your pretty face  from the papers.

06:58.830 --> 07:01.120
你哪都别想去，新来的
You're not going anywhere, fish.

07:01.290 --> 07:02.450
这会发生的
This is gonna happen.

07:02.630 --> 07:06.620
福克斯河州立监狱有半打的守卫  没了工作和退休金
Half a dozen guards  lost their jobs and pensions at Fox River.

07:06.800 --> 07:09.500
另外一半被判缓刑，因为你决定
Another dozen were put on probation  after you decided...

07:09.670 --> 07:13.000
帮助你的男友  和他那七个罪犯兄弟潜逃
...to leave a door open for your boyfriend  and his seven convict pals.

07:13.170 --> 07:16.670
我们不会让这样的事再发生
And we ain't gonna let anything like that  happen again.

07:18.180 --> 07:21.640
不，过来，小亲亲
No. Come here, honey.

07:21.820 --> 07:24.010
别担心，我们不会打到小孩
Don't worry,  we won't hit the baby basket.

07:24.850 --> 07:26.650
- 没错  - 你看她
-Yeah.  -Look at her.

07:27.520 --> 07:28.820
就是这样
That's right.

07:53.680 --> 07:57.120
看来欢迎礼车刚压过你的脸
lt look like that welcome wagon  ran over your face.

07:57.320 --> 07:59.010
看起来很像，对吧？
lt looks that way, huh?

08:00.250 --> 08:04.020
我只是来帮助你适应
l just came by  to help you get adjusted.

08:04.220 --> 08:06.750
如果你需要帮忙  这些警卫我都认识
lf you need something,  l know all these guards.

08:08.360 --> 08:09.690
大部分的人都欠我
Most of them owe me.

08:10.230 --> 08:13.720
很感谢，但我可以照顾自己
l appreciate that,  but l can take care of myself.

08:15.100 --> 08:16.400
是我不对
My bad.

08:16.570 --> 08:19.840
我也不知道为什么  我会觉得你照顾不了自己
l don't know what made me think  you couldn't take care of yourself.

08:22.140 --> 08:24.870
好吧，需要什么就告诉我
All right, well, you need something,  you just ask for me.

08:25.610 --> 08:28.270
大家都叫我老爹
Everybody calls me Daddy.

08:40.230 --> 08:43.250
（迈阿密戴德监狱，男子监狱）

08:56.380 --> 08:58.240
快递
Special delivery.

09:01.080 --> 09:04.810
我们只需要拿点现金  来这里花花
You know, all we need is a little cash  to spread around the place.

09:04.990 --> 09:07.980
我告诉过你，政府冻结我的资产
l told you,  the government's frozen my assets.

09:09.460 --> 09:12.190
你是说你没办法拿到钱？
You telling me  you can't get your hands on any cash?

09:12.960 --> 09:14.620
这是你该做的
That's the least you could do...

09:14.790 --> 09:17.590
因为你不久前还想杀我呢
...considering you was gonna kill me  not too long ago.

09:17.760 --> 09:19.890
再见，泰迪
Goodbye, Theodore.

09:23.040 --> 09:25.030
你以前没被关过
You ain't ever been  incarcerated before...

09:25.210 --> 09:27.830
我也没被关在这里过
...and l ain't ever been  incarcerated here before.

09:28.010 --> 09:29.870
这样说好了，这个残废的囚犯
Let's just say this handicapped con...

09:30.040 --> 09:33.270
尝不到在福克斯河监狱的甜头
...ain't got the juice he had  back in Fox River.

09:34.350 --> 09:39.280
你和我的生活都能过好一点
Your pathetic existence here  could be ameliorated as can my life...

09:39.450 --> 09:40.940
（丹奎迪因谋杀被捕）

09:41.120 --> 09:43.150
只要拿点钱来花花
...all with a little Roberto dinero.

09:43.320 --> 09:47.560
我们的一个朋友被逮捕了
One of our friends has been apprehended  by the authorities.

09:49.860 --> 09:52.420
看来我们有位新邻居
Looks like we've got a new neighbor.

09:53.130 --> 09:56.300
我知道我永远不能活着出去
l'm never gonna get out  of this prison alive, l know that.

09:56.470 --> 09:59.460
我要拉我的敌人当垫背
l wanna bring my enemy down  with me.

09:59.740 --> 10:01.710
我要她死
l want her dead.

10:02.880 --> 10:04.500
（十万元，死）

10:09.820 --> 10:14.010
不管怎样这都需要钱  但你已经没钱了
Either way, it's gonna require capital.  Capital you no longer have.

10:14.190 --> 10:17.320
你知道我的备用基金在哪
My rainy-day fund.  You know where it is.

10:17.490 --> 10:20.580
强纳森，那是你要用来打官司的
Jonathan, l'd assume that  that would be used for your defense.

10:20.760 --> 10:22.590
花再多钱都没用，乔
lt's good money after bad, Joe.

10:22.760 --> 10:27.260
不管我雇用多少律师  都没办法让我离开这里
They're not gonna let me out of here  no matter how many shysters l hire.

10:29.200 --> 10:34.370
把它拿给我们隔壁女监的朋友
Get that to our friend in sister cells  across the compound.

11:27.060 --> 11:28.820
可以坐下吗？
Excuse me.

11:31.230 --> 11:32.890
不智之举
Bad move.

11:35.840 --> 11:38.900
上次碰到她的人  膝盖骨被打断了
Last time someone touched her,  they got a cracked kneecap.

11:59.290 --> 12:01.560
你比我想的还勇敢
You're much braver  than l give you credit for.

12:01.860 --> 12:05.760
- 不是这样，就是你太天真  - 我看起来想跟你说话？
-Either that or you're amazingly naive.  -Do l look like l wanna talk to you?

12:05.930 --> 12:10.060
像你这样的处境应该要找人罩你
Just saying a women in your position  would opt for some protection.

12:10.270 --> 12:14.710
- 加入监狱帮派？我不干  - 不是帮派
-Join a prison gang? l don't think so.  -lt's not a gang, you know.

12:15.010 --> 12:16.070
是家庭
A family.

12:17.880 --> 12:19.970
她们不是平白无故叫她老爹
They don't call her Daddy for nothing.

12:22.380 --> 12:24.110
那是她老婆
That's her wife.

12:24.650 --> 12:25.810
其他是她的小孩
And those are her kids.

12:32.390 --> 12:33.480
你还好吗？
Are you okay?

12:33.660 --> 12:35.820
离我远一点
Stay the hell away from me.

12:37.030 --> 12:40.400
- 我要去医务室  - 没有命令就不能去
-l need to go to the infirmary.  -Can't go without a release form.

12:40.600 --> 12:44.370
我喉头紧缩，下巴越来越紧
l'm having muscle contractions  in my throat and my jaw's tightening up.

12:44.540 --> 12:46.870
是食用番木鳖鹼，老鼠药
lt's strychnine ingestion,  it's rat poison.

12:47.040 --> 12:49.010
是公家的干酪，习惯吧
That's government cheese,  get used to it.

12:49.180 --> 12:53.640
如果我十五分钟内没到医院  我和我的孩子都会死
lf l don't get to the hospital the next 1 5  minutes, l will die and my baby will die.

12:53.810 --> 12:55.470
拜托
Please.

12:55.850 --> 12:59.050
你何不让她去看医生？
Bo, why don't you let her go  see the doc?

13:04.420 --> 13:06.020
拜托
Please.

13:07.360 --> 13:10.920
我是考勒，有犯人要到医务室
This is Cowler. We have an inmate  going to the infirmary.

13:18.370 --> 13:21.360
我们即时做活性炭灌洗
We were able to administer  the charcoal lavage in time.

13:21.540 --> 13:24.200
你和宝宝都会没事
You and your baby are gonna be okay.

13:25.710 --> 13:28.770
番木鳖鹼不会自己跑到我的肉块里
The strychnine didn't get in my meat loaf  all by itself, right?

13:29.080 --> 13:31.570
你需要跟典狱长说
Well, then you need to talk  to the warden about it.

13:35.150 --> 13:37.280
要不要跟我说你的脸怎么了？
Then how about talking to me  about your face?

13:37.460 --> 13:39.290
要不要跟我说是怎么弄的？
You wanna tell me  how that happened?

13:41.160 --> 13:43.460
我打篮球时弄伤的
l caught an elbow playing basketball.

13:45.930 --> 13:48.920
我们应该讨论你的情况
We should discuss your situation.

13:49.100 --> 13:52.800
我想你应该知道  这不会是一般的怀孕
l'm sure you've ascertained, this isn't  gonna be a run-of-the-mill pregnancy.

13:52.970 --> 13:54.630
- 我会在这里生吗？  - 不会
-Do l deliver in here?  -No.

13:54.810 --> 13:57.780
生的那一天会让你坐上救护车
The day we induce,  we'll secure you in an ambulance.

13:57.940 --> 14:01.280
带你到邻近的圣露西亚医院  我们会封锁一个房间
Take you to Saint Lucia down the road.  We'll cordon off a room.

14:01.450 --> 14:03.940
你生产时会有三个持枪的狱警驻守
There'll be three armed guards  when you give birth.

14:04.320 --> 14:06.650
我可以看宝宝吗？
Do l get to see my baby?

14:06.820 --> 14:08.790
抱走之前你有三十分钟
You'll have 30 minutes  before we take it.

14:12.890 --> 14:14.720
这个过程我已经看过好几次了
l've seen this process a dozen times.

14:15.300 --> 14:18.630
母亲回来之后  大多都难以承受那种低落
After the mothers come back here,  the depression's almost unbearable.

14:18.800 --> 14:19.960
我的建议是
My advice...

14:20.470 --> 14:23.630
如果你把自己想成  代理孕母会好一点
...it's less messy, if you just think  of yourself as a surrogate.

14:36.080 --> 14:37.450
是的？
Yeah?

14:37.620 --> 14:39.240
麦可，我是布鲁菲力普
Michael, it's Blue Phillips.

14:39.420 --> 14:42.910
听着，你太太刚才发生意外
Listen,  your wife had an incident earlier today.

14:43.090 --> 14:44.420
有人想要毒死她
Someone tried to poison her.

14:45.290 --> 14:48.120
- 你在说什么？  - 麦可，你注意听
-What are you talking about?  -Michael, l need you to focus.

14:48.290 --> 14:50.490
你知道可能是谁？
Do you have any idea  who might've done--?

14:50.660 --> 14:52.150
麦可？
Michael?

14:52.600 --> 14:54.120
麦可
Michael.

14:55.200 --> 14:57.140
好的，让他进来
All right, let him in.

15:08.050 --> 15:11.780
如果我有一张名单  上面写着谁可能会来看我
lf l had a list of all the people  who might come to visit me...

15:11.950 --> 15:14.550
你的名字可能会在
...your name would be at the bottom,  somewhere below...

15:14.750 --> 15:16.980
在耶稣和史酷比之后
...Jesus Christ and Scooby-Doo.

15:17.160 --> 15:18.990
今天有人想毒死莎拉
Someone tried to poison Sara today.

15:19.460 --> 15:20.480
还好没事
Mercy.

15:20.660 --> 15:23.360
只有你才会坏到
Only you would be depraved enough...

15:23.530 --> 15:26.690
认为杀害一个无辜的母亲  和她肚子里的孩子
...to think that killing an innocent  woman and her unborn child...

15:26.870 --> 15:29.990
能让你在死刑之前  获得一点宁静
...would bring you some kind of peace,  before your execution.

15:30.170 --> 15:33.070
莎拉怀孕了？
Sara is with child?

15:33.270 --> 15:35.040
恭喜
Congratulations.

15:35.210 --> 15:38.230
这像国庆日和圣诞节  合二为一的感觉
This is like the 4th of July  and Christmas rolled into one.

15:38.410 --> 15:43.680
我以父亲对父亲的身份  求你放了她
l'm asking you, father to father,  to leave her alone.

