Thank you for the invite.

18:58.680 --> 19:00.670
我很高兴
lt's always a pleasure.

19:02.520 --> 19:05.280
亚历，这个裁定可以再议
You know, Alex,  this ruling can be revisited...

19:05.890 --> 19:08.250
如果你能证明
...if you were able  to sufficiently demonstrate...

19:08.420 --> 19:11.190
你有多投入一生为民服务
...just how committed you are  to a life of service.

19:11.520 --> 19:15.120
