19:28.570 --> 19:31.240
如果史柯菲能够
Well, obviously,  if Scofield were to be able...

19:31.410 --> 19:33.810
成功策划另一次越狱
...to pull off this plot  of another breakout...

19:34.010 --> 19:37.040
