...the public embarrassment  would be immense to the bureau.

19:37.220 --> 19:40.620
如果有人能提供可靠的线索
So having someone to get us  credible information...

19:40.790 --> 19:42.810
对我们来说非常有用
...that would be worth something  to us.

19:43.020 --> 19:45.890
维特力探员会驻守迈阿密  他是你的联络人
Agent Wheatley is set up in Miami.  He would be your contact.

19:46.060 --> 19:48.150
