Give me a reason to give it to you.

20:07.180 --> 20:09.110
把她救出来后你有什么计划？
What's your plan  after we break her out?

20:09.280 --> 20:11.310
- 我们又要逃亡？  - 重要的事先做
-We on the run again?  -First thing's first.

20:11.480 --> 20:13.450
- 我们去救她出来  - 老大
-Let's get her out of there.  -Hey, papi.

20:13.620 --> 20:16.990
逮捕莎拉的那个探员  在外面监视我们
The Fed that arrested Sara?  He's outside staking us out.

20:18.490 --> 20:21.320
如果你们担心又要趟入浑水
Look, if you're worried  about getting into trouble again...

20:21.490 --> 20:23.660
就回去芝加哥  回到家人的身边
...go back to Chicago.  Go back to your family.

20:23.830 --> 20:24.990
我会理解的
l'll understand.

20:25.160 --> 20:26.190
你说笑吗？
Are you kidding me?

20:26.370 --> 20:29.600
在我们经历这么多事后  难道我会不顾你跟莎拉？
After all we been through, l'm gonna  leave you here and Sara there?

20:29.770 --> 20:33.100
闭嘴，不要再提了  那些是什么？
Shut up and don't bring it up again.  What's all that?

20:33.270 --> 20:34.470
剪报
Newspaper clippings.

20:34.640 --> 20:37.270
包含七个不同的逃狱计划
Covering seven different  escape attempts...

20:37.440 --> 20:39.930
是过去六十年  发生在迈阿密戴德州立监狱的计划
...from Miami-Dade State Pen,  over the last 60 years.

20:40.110 --> 20:42.980
