None of them--  None of them successful.

20:43.280 --> 20:45.770
我们看了之后  就知道哪些方法不可行
So we read them all  and we learn what not to do.

20:45.950 --> 20:49.510
监狱官员学了很多  他们重新评估改进
The prison officials learned a lot.  They re-evaluated, they retrofitted.

20:49.690 --> 20:52.180
这座监狱根本没办法逃脱
The prison's practically escape-proof.

20:52.360 --> 20:54.620
- 你还好吗？  - 我很好
-You all right?  -l'm fine.

20:55.490 --> 20:58.550
好，如果我们进不去  那么下降的方式呢？
Okay, so if we can't go through,  what if we go down?

20:58.730 --> 21:01.030
我们跳伞进去，降到监狱中
Like, down into the prison.  We parachute in.

21:01.700 --> 21:03.170
- 好  - 没错
-Yeah.  -Yeah.

21:03.340 --> 21:05.130
- 找到她，带她出来  - 你在说笑？
-Find her, get out.  -Are you kidding?

21:05.300 --> 21:07.240
- 我是认真的  - 这根本是自杀
-l'm serious.  -That's suicide.

21:07.410 --> 21:10.530
