l ain't even gonna touch you.

22:00.960 --> 22:03.900
我负责汽车修理场
See, l run the motor-pool detail  in here.

22:04.060 --> 22:07.060
我在想如果你想要点新鲜空气
l was thinking, if you wanna  get yourself a little fresh air...

22:07.230 --> 22:10.070
而不必担心被困在后面
...and not have to worry  about getting stuck in the back...

22:10.240 --> 22:13.470
就来跟我工作
...then you can come  and work with me.

23:08.930 --> 23:10.450
你是出现在我婚礼的探员
You're the Fed from my wedding.

23:10.630 --> 23:13.460
- 叫我维特力探员  - 可以用来叫你的词可多了
-Call me Agent Wheatley.  -l could call you a lot of things.

23:13.630 --> 23:15.030
- 你去哪？  - 海洋世界
-Where you headed?  -Sea World.

23:15.230 --> 23:17.530
- 迈阿密没有海洋世界  - 我的损失
-Sea World. There isn't one in Miami.  -My loss.

23:17.740 --> 23:21.730
