23:37.360 --> 23:39.760
我的职责是确保她待在里面
lt's my job to make sure  that she stays there.

23:40.530 --> 23:43.890
你的那些兄弟呢？
So where's all your little buddies?

23:50.000 --> 23:52.770
好，干冰多丢一点
All right. Drop in more dry ice.

24:06.220 --> 24:07.580
